column5: Today is TG's birthday and to celibrate he took off early this am with his lovely bride to visit his favorite lake in Northwestern Ontario. Beside the fact that he will spend most of the day on the road on his birthday I couldn't think of to many places I would want to head to on my birthday Not going to mentioned how old he is today   but I hope I get around like he does at that age. I guess if I keep hanging around him he'll get me on the path to healthy  Happy Birthday TG and hope you enjoy many more!  Cheers!
hope ya have a great birthday connie, have a great time up there in paradise.  jason
Happy B-Day, hope you have a great day!
Happy Birthday Connie  Hope you got what you wanted today, be it fish or otherwise  Joey
A very happy birthday Connie, have a great one. Look forward to the trip report when you return.

Thanks everybody.  Left home Wednesday at 10:15 a.m. and made it 875 miles to Eau Claire Wisconsin first night.   Got to Sportsman's a couple of hours ago and we're going after some Walleyes.  Joey, I'll work on that.  Hope to get more than I can eat.  Connie
Happy Birthday Connie. You're a good man and deserve all the good things that happen to you. Those good things don't come to you by accident. What goes 'round, comes 'round.  Be well my friend.
Happy Birthday and Best Fishes to you Connie!!!
